{"tid":1745834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最緊要係齊！齊！齊！區選大家齊投票","createTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:26:19.000Z","uid":41342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be198600ae5bee9a93e5342524338663b8a0d192","tid":1745834,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"1. 唔好投廢票或白票<br />\n我知唔少人話唔可以跟政府區選個制度玩<br />\n投白票或廢票都可以顯示自己既立場<br />\n仲可以透過呢啲票數凸顯對政制既失望同埋令當選既人無認受性<br />\n<br />\n但留意一點<br />\n無認受性還無認受性<br />\n對家既拎到既資源唔會同佢既認受性有掛勾<br />\n即係你知我知佢係垃圾 但仍然佢係可以舐盡資源<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好唔投泛民<br />\n即使你知我知 泛民賣港人 有投過棄權<br />\n咁多年投佢地無用  唔通今次投佢地有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n但要知既係  建制贏咗 對我地更加無好處<br />\n我知大家要含淚投 但含淚既背後 係咪真係有得揀先？<br />\n我見好多都係兩個候選人 一泛民一建制咁選<br />\n而有啲三個候選人<br />\n有多一個揀  我無意見 亦唔想叫大家含淚<br />\n但得兩個候選人揀的話  你淚流成河都要投泛民<br />\n<br />\n因為政局有改變 大家先會繼續有出路<br />\n<br />\n假設當多泛民當選  首先會知佢地至少某立場都會照住港人角度去諗 而亦當佢地做得勢 及後做得衰  咁到時起碼會諗 「大家要改變模式」  香港既出路先唔會去到無限loop<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家齊心地支持自己人 先屌走建制派<br />\n其他既問題係後話！"},{"pid":"1ac51081f82fabe18e42bebd63f713565826b4da","tid":1745834,"uid":15266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fd9ea2343e71be0ba706f2fdbe5539a3de3394","tid":1745834,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67c56dd46729035c56b03fc0273dc0094ca79a0","tid":1745834,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=700a15c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=08033eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=17cd9a59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=1408bf57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c77f04ba0861e3e07827bda6eb200703a12178d4","tid":1745834,"uid":52058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"仲要叫身邊人投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉攏更多人變黃<br />\n奪取十八區議會主權"},{"pid":"e31c2a8f8a96a0b188df208eeff82f5a68a22eef","tid":1745834,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 